data.description: Welcome to your new home at 9063 Jimmy Lee Circle! Nestled in the heart of Jonesboro, Georgia, this charming property offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience.    This spacious 4 bedroom, 2-and-a-half-bathroom home boasts 2,278 square feet of living space, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment. From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright, airy and grand atmosphere, thanks to the 2 story foyer!     The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar, making it the perfect place to gather and enjoy time with you’re family and friends while whipping up delicious meals. The adjacent dining area offers plenty of room for gatherings and opens to the living room, ideal for cozying up by the fireplace on chilly evenings.    Step outside to your own private oasis, where you'll find a spacious backyard with plenty of room for outdoor activities and al fresco dining. With the seller leaving behind both the pergola and the shed providing you with ample storage and shade during the summer. Whether you're hosting summer barbecues or enjoying a quiet morning coffee, this backyard is sure to impress.    Back inside, the spacious bedrooms provide the perfect retreat at the end of a long day, with plush carpeting, ample closet space, and plenty of natural light. The primary suite features a luxurious ensuite bathroom, complete with a soaking tub and separate shower, offering a spa-like experience right at home.    Conveniently located near shopping, dining, parks, and schools, this home offers easy access to everything Jonesboro has to offer. Don't miss your chance to make this beautiful property your own – schedule a showing today!
